ðŸ§  What to Focus On
When generating code or guidance:
Prioritize speed, security, and scalability
Use React (Vite + Tailwind) for the frontend
Use Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Edge Functions) as backend
Integrate Python AI microservice (FastAPI) for AI chatbot logic
Include QR code generation and scanning (using qrcode.react)
Implement AES-256 encryption, JWT auth, and Row-Level Security for privacy
Optimize for mobile-first experience (low bandwidth, offline-ready)

Support user and admin roles

Make the design modern, accessible, and responsive

